sequenceDiagram
    participant E as Engine
    participant Src as Source<br/>(Kafka/file/Delta)
    participant Off as offsets/<br/>(checkpoint)
    participant Sink as Sink<br/>(Delta/etc.)
    participant Com as commits/<br/>(checkpoint)
    E->>Src: Request offsets [start_N, end_N]
    Src-->>E: offsets
    E->>Off: WAL: persist (N, start, end)
    E->>E: Process micro-batch N
    E->>Sink: Write batch N (tagged batch_id=N)
    Note over Sink: Idempotent sink dedups by batch_id
    Sink-->>E: ack
    E->>Com: WAL: mark batch N committed
    Note over E,Com: Crash before this -> redo<br/>(sink dedup keeps it exactly-once)
